# 🚗 CarFact — Armenian VIN Check Telegram Bot

🧾 Check the true history of any used vehicle by its VIN directly inside Telegram.

## 🔧 Features

- ✅ VIN validation & parsing
- 📦 FastAPI backend (Python)
- 🛢 PostgreSQL log storage (SQLAlchemy)
- 📲 Telegram bot with inline keyboards & commands
- 🧠 Command: `/start`, `/history`, direct VIN input
- 💾 Request history per user
- 🔐 Ready for future monetization

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Python 3.11
- FastAPI + Uvicorn
- PostgreSQL + SQLAlchemy
- python-telegram-bot 20.x
- Render.com (for hosting)

## 🚀 Local Development

```bash
git clone git@github.com:brainforcegit/vin-bot.git
cd vin-bot
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn backend.main:app --reload
